up.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74f87307541454ba5795b87d02ce66c1a795a58","tid":1812232,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a2b7c2d233d54c3cc044b7fab29547c051db2c0","tid":1812232,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">振興黃色經濟 拒絕幫襯建制</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府正用盡一切手段迫企業歸邊，為示威者樹敵，為求社會各界與抗爭人士割蓆<br />\n<br />\n同時黑警透過非法濫捕，圖阻嚇港人和平表達訴求，損害港人自由，有違基本法28條原意<br />\n<br />\n比你捉到便衣狗係為咗養成捉鬼文化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6wEt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6wEt9.jpg&h=75dfc14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avbtvJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavbtvJ0.jpg&h=e1c98503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊心祝福<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug7anh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug7anh2.png&h=2bf968e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98432685ffe2e0153c0dab0b8faeb393b2ad862e","tid":1812232,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:29:46.000Z","msg":"只有on9先會繼續放任班黑警卜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i